                            <comment id="73848" author="yujian" created="Thu, 19 Dec 2013 15:36:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lustre client: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_3/41/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_3/41/&lt;/a&gt; (2.3.0)&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre server: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_4/69/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_4/69/&lt;/a&gt; (2.4.2 RC1)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity test 154 hit the same failure:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3c82ea6e-685e-11e3-a16f-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3c82ea6e-685e-11e3-a16f-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="65686" author="yujian" created="Wed, 4 Sep 2013 05:28:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lustre client: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_3/41/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_3/41/&lt;/a&gt; (2.3.0)&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre server: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_4/44/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_4/44/&lt;/a&gt; (2.4.1 RC1)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity test 154 hit the same failure:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cde5bab8-14f3-11e3-9828-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cde5bab8-14f3-11e3-9828-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59428" author="utopiabound" created="Tue, 28 May 2013 14:19:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Should I submit a patch on b2_3 to fix this?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59422" author="utopiabound" created="Tue, 28 May 2013 13:19:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In change &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5298&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5298&lt;/a&gt; the prohibition to setxattr on .lustre and .lustre/fid was removed so the 2.3.0 check to ensure it fails is no longer valid for 2.4 MDTs (2.3.64 and following).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59294" author="adilger" created="Fri, 24 May 2013 17:46:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like there is a bug in the test script, where it is using the filename instead of the FID for open-by-fid in some cases. Not sure why it is inconsistent. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My guess is the unknown sequence error is because the &quot;fid&quot; that is passed coincidentally has &quot;f&quot; at the start, and somehow gets interpreted as 0xf00000400?  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If that is not the case, then there may be a more serious underlying problem, so we&apos;d like some investigation (hopefully today) to determine the root cause. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
